Allocates a reference-counted slice and moves `v`'s items into it.

# Example

```
# use std::rc::Rc;
let unique: Vec<i32> = vec![1, 2, 3];
let shared: Rc<[i32]> = Rc::from(unique);
assert_eq!(&[1, 2, 3], &shared[..]);
```
